leaves.text: Wait List, Reservation, and Loyalty management for restaurants

nodes.text: Remain in control while serving more diners. Accept reservations from your website or the Hostme mobile application. Leverage our unique "Hybrid" reservation mode to protect your restaurant from no-shows. Avoid double booking with the Hostme conflict validation algorithm.

Improve host efficiency and maximize seat utilization. Create a floor map of any complexity. Track restaurant occupancy. Assign reservations or walk-ins to a table in one click. Avoid double booking with our conflict validation algorithm..

Seat parties faster and increase efficiency at the host stand. Notify guests when their table is ready using their phone. Track who waited an excessively long time and reward them with loyalty points or a free drink. Eliminate costly pager losses.

Loyalty program that matches your restaurant and your guests. Get your loyalty program up-and-running in no time. Let your guests enroll while they are waiting for their table or right after they are seated. Fill tables on days when it's usually slow with customized reward rules.
Learn from Kafe Leopolds how to manage crowd in popular places
